BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:568@bwa-calendar
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260605
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260606
SUMMARY:BWA: Parent/Carer Coffee Morning -  Supporting Your Child with BIG Emotions
DESCRIPTION:The Education Wellbeing Service hosts a coffee morning at BWA to discuss managing big emotions in children.\n\nThe Education Wellbeing Service will be hosting a coffee morning at BWA. The main focus will be supporting your child to manage big emotions, understanding emotion regulation, and learning practical strategies. Provided by Battersea Education Wellbeing Service.
CATEGORIES:WELLBEING
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:570@bwa-calendar
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260601
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260602
SUMMARY:BWA: Parents Morning
DESCRIPTION:Parents are invited to a welcome reception and classroom activities.\n\nParents are invited to a welcome reception from 8:50am to 9:10am, followed by classroom activities from 9:15am to 10:00am. Only one parent per child is permitted. Note: CM2B/Y6B session is postponed to the final French focus week.
CATEGORIES:COMMUNITY
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:581@bwa-calendar
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260621
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260623
SUMMARY:BWA: APL Summer Kermesse
DESCRIPTION:APL's annual Summer Kermesse at school featuring games, food, and celebrations. The big one! More details to come!\n\nThe big one! Let’s celebrate the height of summer and the end of the school year together at our annual Kermesse. Expect games, food, and plenty of sunshine as we bring the whole school family together. More details to come!
CATEGORIES:PTA
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:578@bwa-calendar
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260703
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260705
SUMMARY:BWA: Hair Day
DESCRIPTION:BWA Crazy Hair Day: PTA/APL's Crazy Hair Day for both schools, time to get creative!\n\nChildren can come to school with their craziest hair styles! Whether it’s rainbow mohawks, glittery spikes, animal-shaped hair, or colorful braids, we want to see it all! \nWe encourage you to get involved and help your child create their wild hairstyle. Let’s make this a memorable day for everyone! PTA/APL's Crazy Hair Day for both schools, time to get creative!
CATEGORIES:PTA
END:VEVENT
